00:20:22,050 --> 00:20:24,670
Do you know when today's story
ran as manga in JUMP?

444
00:20:24,670 --> 00:20:26,690
It was in June of last year.

445
00:20:26,690 --> 00:20:28,850
Back then, it was a big hit.

446
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:32,170
